sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as vllm-orchestrator-gateway<br/>8090/TCP HTTP
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8085/TCP HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over Client,Orchestrator: Flow 1: Non-Streaming Chat Completion with Detection

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>Authorization: Bearer {token}<br/>{"model":"...","messages":[...],"stream":false}
    Note over Gateway: Injects route-specific detector<br/>config (input/output detector maps)<br/>into request payload
    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Authorization: Bearer {token} (forwarded)<br/>x-forwarded-* headers (forwarded)<br/>Conditional mTLS (client cert if present)
    Orchestrator-->>Gateway: HTTP 200 JSON Response<br/>{"choices":[...],"detections":{...}}
    Note over Gateway: If detections found AND<br/>fallback_message configured:<br/>replace response content<br/>with fallback message
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTP 200 JSON Response<br/>{"choices":[{"message":{"content":"..."}}]}

    Note over Client,Orchestrator: Flow 2: Streaming Chat Completion with Detection (SSE)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>Authorization: Bearer {token}<br/>{"model":"...","messages":[...],"stream":true}
    Note over Gateway: Injects route-specific detector<br/>config into request payload
    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Authorization: Bearer {token} (forwarded)<br/>Conditional mTLS
    loop SSE Stream Chunks
        Orchestrator-->>Gateway: data: {"choices":[{"delta":{"content":"..."}}],"detections":{...}}
        Note over Gateway: Parse each SSE chunk;<br/>if detections found AND<br/>fallback_message configured:<br/>replace delta content,<br/>set finish_reason="stop"
        Gateway-->>Client: data: {"choices":[{"delta":{"content":"..."}}]}
    end
    Orchestrator-->>Gateway: data: [DONE]
    Gateway-->>Client: data: [DONE]
